            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and dice your <strong>carrot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
