            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter alternative </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and <strong>diced carrot </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Combine 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>milk alternative</strong> and 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[340ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>in a measuring jug with your<strong> Marmite </strong>and <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>– this is your <strong>Marmite stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
