    {
      "instruction": "<p>Shred your <strong>meat-free chick'n </strong>using two forks, then add to the <strong>pie mix</strong> and stir it all together</p><p>Transfer the <strong>pie mix </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> (or two!)</p><p>Top the pie mix with the <strong>rolled pastry </strong>and crimp round the edge with a fork</p><p>Score a cross in the middle of the pastry and put it in the oven for 15-18 min or until puffed up, golden and cooked through – this is your <strong>plant-based chick’n pie</strong></p>",
